<SYNC Start=362230><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=369437><P Class=KRCC>
<font color=gray>카카...시...
<SYNC Start=371103><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=388446><P Class=KRCC>
(린...)
<SYNC Start=389782><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=392454><P Class=KRCC>
